{"tid":1681902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"党鐵佔八達通八成股份，我哋係咪仲要日日嘟咭嘟得咁爽？","createTime":"2019-10-29T17:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T17:40:39.000Z","uid":283929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58c6c0cd71168e36c7783b0ae975c1635f319c87","tid":1681902,"uid":283929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:13:04.000Z","msg":"講緊黃色經濟圈喎！點解冇人留意黨鐵係八達通最大股東嘅？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1t59a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1t59a6.jpg&h=ced41eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《申請成為八達通商戶有甚麼收費？》<br />\n收費包括按每項交易收取指定百分比的費用、八達通器材成本和類型檢定測試費。<br />\n<br />\n👆🏼八達通網站冇講清楚收商戶幾多錢，但係佢哋推廣緊嘅O! ePay 就收費如下：<br />\n<br />\n行業類型\t銀行賬戶資金轉賬費<br />\n(由2018年9月30日起開始生效)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">非交通</span>\t轉賬金額的1.5％，如轉賬金額的1.5％少於港幣1元，則為港幣1元（視情況而定）<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">交通</span>（例如：的士)\t轉賬金額的1％，如轉賬金額的1％少於港幣1元，則為港幣1元（視情況而定）<br />\n<br />\n即係每次你嘟八達通坐車、買嘢、食嘢，黨鐵就自動有錢袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲記唔記得831、窩藏運送黑警、最需要佢嗰陣時落閘放狗... 仲要咁益佢？ 我哋冇得揀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/corporate/about-octopus/profile/structure/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.octopus.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fcorporate%2Fabout-octopus%2Fprofile%2Fstructure%2Findex.html&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsgx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=e9d4e552\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/corporate/about-octopus/profile/structure/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"b021bb3b011072806ab1f63f0bb8b00e368e7725","tid":1681902,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLXe8W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLXe8W.jpg&h=d3761788&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7831b38c971d94d6097cfad75cb268dcae59ab84","tid":1681902,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:19:43.000Z","msg":"平時用開paywave當八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ac22af1b218e910ff7d1595a9af58ee1734046","tid":1681902,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:21:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3dc4d4608f7c22f4862f7a09e95132d148ef7b5","tid":1681902,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"有得揀就用信用卡<br />\n<br />\n搭車冇得揀先會用八達通"},{"pid":"b436bb40ce97c4cec4e0cd2f0e8912f57ecea204","tid":1681902,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"警世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今時今日<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: orange;\">有其他選擇嘅情況</span><br />\n你仍俾正價搭黨鐵<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">你每搭1蚊<br />\n嗰1蚊就係資助佢地運狗<br />\n同埋出賣港人</span><br />\n你良心過唔過意得去<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黨鐵仲唔笑你班人無骨氣咩</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkkdJhO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkkdJhO.jpg&h=58322cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55r07Ku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55r07Ku.jpg&h=b2de0f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRmXTUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRmXTUi.jpg&h=1b242b55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"531078513b9d8c42415474a8c63dc690d2660887","tid":1681902,"uid":283929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3dc4d4608f7c22f4862f7a09e95132d148ef7b5","tid":1681902,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"有得揀就